			<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="p:8;73:7">In 2022, I wrote quite a few small articles based on my experiences with various DITA
				publishing customizations and they are all linked in this overview post: <xref href="dita_ot_publishing_customizations_overview.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="xref:4;75:62" type="topic"><?ditaot gentext?>Publishing Customizations</xref>.</p>
			<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="p:9;76:7">I also wrote an article about the various ways that we support the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="b:30;76:77">DITA Open Toolkit</b>
