			<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="p:10;78:7">Our client and friend <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="b:31;78:32">Chris Papademetrious</b> also submitted an article about enhancing
				DITA Open Toolkit project files: <xref href="preprocessing_ditaot_project_files.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="xref:6;80:53" type="topic"><?ditaot gentext?>Preprocessing DITA-OT Project Files</xref>.</p>
			<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="p:11;81:7"> These articles were also presented at the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/blog_2022_retrospective.dita" xtrc="b:32;81:53">DITA Open Toolkit Day</b> 2022 along other
